The whole thing hinges on TRUST. I have a lot of EVP I&#39;ve recorded, one of
which blatantly shows something &quot;paranormal&quot; occurring by actual evidence
available. But anyone listening, not trusting the originator, can say it was
faked. There&#39;s no way to prove it wasn&#39;t, to their satisfaction. If I were
to send these EVP to them, they&#39;d just wave it off as made up or altered by
me, I&#39;m sure - which ISN&#39;T the case. But these guys have no idea who to
trust and who not to trust. There ARE some trustworthy people out there.

Zack

